# Time Capsule Diary ðŸ•°

A Firebase-based web app to store diary entries that unlock at a future date.

## Features
- Save text entries and photos
- Auto-unlock with sound alerts
- View and delete unlocked entries

## Tech Stack
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Firebase Firestore & Hosting

## Setup
1. Clone this repo
2. Replace Firebase config in script.js with your own
3. Open index.html in your browser

